{"tid":333940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"毓民最後的一個月 過得最高興就是反骨仔靳民知！","createTime":"2017-07-24T09:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T11:58:10.000Z","uid":49388,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca70bd92626b4ae1520186ef9c6bcf13a00b2978","tid":333940,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"Marco Toscanini:<br />\n<br />\n還說選舉？<br />\n<br />\n昨日書展有一中年支持者，<br />\n語重深長，<br />\n對毓民重提選舉&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n記得去年選前的星期二三，<br />\n凌晨三四點，<br />\n我還是在和一高人通電話，<br />\n分析得出的結論是，<br />\n九西的選情極不容易。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個方案，<br />\n我只說過一句，<br />\n就是預早將 MyRadio 大房，<br />\n準備為記者會場地。<br />\n竟然，<br />\n一語成讖。<br />\n<br />\n九龍西輸了，<br />\n記者會完了，<br />\n大房關了燈，<br />\n頭脹發燒，<br />\n我一個人坐在漆黑空空冷冷的大房睡著了。<br />\n<br />\n那種感覺極端難受。<br />\n<br />\n但是，<br />\n於多人眼中看到，<br />\n有一兩人的態度是：&ldquo;鄭松泰贏，毓民輸都無所謂&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n毓辦最後的一個月，<br />\n過得最開心的，<br />\n滿心歡喜的，<br />\n就是靳民知。<br />\n<br />\n當大家看清鄭已完的咀臉時，<br />\n絕不要忘記靳民知。<br />\n<br />\n靳民知、李樂恒，<br />\n我等著睇你地成為&ldquo;人肉避孕套&rdquo;，<br />\n如何被人用完即棄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/173452_657003724abea9cffdd3b79529d08402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F173452_657003724abea9cffdd3b79529d08402.jpg&h=a1565dcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"116766f5eeb28840d8caf28c89a9425a1daae222","tid":333940,"uid":57035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"阿勒真係辣殺嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3883c584b9a0342885de625b77e7b8d2cdc5234e","tid":333940,"uid":51469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"阿靳既人生目標就係議員助理<br />\n梗係唔介意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3c987a844a20d45bddb03eee51f0b9cb0df9db","tid":333940,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"阿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee522d68376cf030ec833c8918fca5d93c50493","tid":333940,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"社運垃圾"},{"pid":"a5e78b17348d6308c89003c778a2e67ac57f158e","tid":333940,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"阿勒個樣咁正氣都俾人批鬥"},{"pid":"cc460e61bbecdb68fd29719e7dd35250a36ab8ac","tid":333940,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿勒個樣咁正氣都俾人批鬥</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://bimg.hitttt.com/dd8_20150422/6767_1ad0059d5e0d527a25b3265135d05340_W1213_024_N_cny150417b_020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbimg.hitttt.com%2Fdd8_20150422%2F6767_1ad0059d5e0d527a25b3265135d05340_W1213_024_N_cny150417b_020.jpg&h=09cf9518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e89f6481efd36299dff0c9500751f8c6a67a3105","tid":333940,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"靳民知都係西瓜靠大邊"},{"pid":"bcace26f39f85dffca6a94179121c4e66e0f4bd0","tid":333940,"uid":65649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"佢成班講野gur埋一舊，毓民都同你同台做節目，比d野你做等你有飯食，依家成班反轉豬肚<br />\n<br />\n食相太難看了"},{"pid":"faf7a26b0b54e21f234278fadb29cce8ccf76913","tid":333940,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢成班講野gur埋一舊，毓民都同你同台做節目，比d野你做等你有飯食，依家成班反轉豬肚<br />\n<br />\n食相太難看了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢留係myradio做忠臣就唔使憂啦⋯⋯<br />\n而家身敗名裂<br />\n最多四年玩完"},{"pid":"b2db406d5dff1fa2b129740a0de0b3d21e0c6117","tid":333940,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢成班講野gur埋一舊，毓民都同你同台做節目，比d野你做等你有飯食，依家成班反轉豬肚<br />\n<br />\n食相太難看了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢留係myradio做忠臣就唔使憂啦⋯⋯<br